OL,5, Bosses at three of the UK's water      
OL,6, companies have decided not to take     
OL,7, their annual bonuses after widespread  
OL,8, public criticism over sewage pollution.
OL,10,FThames Water's Sarah Bentley said it   
OL,11,Fdid not "feel right" to take the bonus,
OL,12,Falong with South West Water's Susan    
OL,13,FDavy and Yorkshire Water's Nicola Shaw.
OL,15,FThe BBC has contacted the eight other  
OL,16,Fmajor water companies to see if they   
OL,17,Fwill follow suit.                      
OL,19,FCampaigners have called for all UK     
OL,20,Fwater firm CEOs to waive their bonuses.
